<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_assembly_design_arm.Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint">
 A <b>Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint</b> is an assignment of a <express_ref linkend="Network_functional_design_view:arm:Network_functional_design_view_arm.Functional_unit"/> in a <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Design_composition_path"/> to its <b>implementation</b> in an <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembly_joint"/>. 
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_assembly_design_arm.Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint.implementation">
the <b>implementation</b> specifies the <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembly_joint"/> for the 
<b>Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_assembly_design_arm.Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint.functional_design_definition_path">
the <b>functional_design_definition_path</b> specifies the <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Design_composition_path"/> for the <b>Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_assembly_design_arm.Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint.ur:UR1">
The <b>functional_design_definition_path</b> shall be unique within a population of 
<b>Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_joint</b>.
</ext_description>
